      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated precision. Under the hood, the S54 inline-six features a meticulously maintained valvetrain and individual throttle bodies that deliver instantaneous response. All critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains rigid and factory-true, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a perfectly dialed variable M differential lock. With an immaculate undercarriage and original suspension geometry intact, this vehicle offers the mechanical purity and tactile feedback of a showroom-fresh icon.",
